{"tid":1612713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"於2014年，一名男子以一己之力癱瘓港鐵半小時","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T14:47:19.000Z","uid":133495,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0852ddfcaf638f90dbf895fde1157f7f0e80b7f5","tid":1612713,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140203%2F00410_097.html&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=e2900d34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html</a><br />\n<br />\n金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難。"},{"pid":"7e93db840d05614f6516da4794a470b22df97fd0","tid":1612713,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c059b9898889fe74be64cee7da7f96841322ace3","tid":1612713,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33144e9fe16d989596c05bb6fb74870d50ddade","tid":1612713,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e93f84e12c976739fd854c4adc28150b4919096","tid":1612713,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a7d1327a730ae8a52ab5a6939ddc68014c1c22","tid":1612713,"uid":133495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"